The paper deals with the problem of compressive phase retrieval, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT) and machine learning (cs.LG) that has applications in computer vision (cs.CV) and signal processing (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the use of graph codes, which is a topic in social and information networks (cs.SI).
